overview: Jung-hoon is happily dating his cute and lovely girlfriend Ye-ju. She is about to spend a hot day at Ye-ju's empty house.. She meets Min-ji, her roommate, who visited Ye-ju while she was sleeping. Min-ji knows the past of Jeong-hoon, who worked at her hoppa in the past.
title: 18 Temptation of Hwayoung, a beginner model
